                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-sm-3">
                                                    <h3 class="heading">News</h3>
                                                    <ul class="nav mega-vertical-nav">
                                                        <li><a href="http://www.thepuppymillproject.org/">Puppy Mills</a></li>
                                                        <li><a href="http://www.aspca.org/animal-cruelty">Animal Cruelty</a></li>
                                                        <li><a href="http://www.avmf.org/whatwedo/animal-disaster-relief-and-response-fund">Animal Disaster Relief</a></li>
                                                        
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-sm-3">
                                                    <h3 class="heading">Our Business</h3>
